ABOUT SCENTIDO

A WORLD OF AROMATIC LUXURIES

Allow your mind to wander through the gates of seduction.

Dip yourself into the poetic art of perfumery.
Let it caress your senses and narrate a fragrant story.

Let the world stop and follow the fragrance to its source at SCENTIDO Niche Perfumery.

A scent can mean many things, but it is always an expression.


At SCENTIDO, we want you to express yourself through a deeply sensorial experience.


Explore the art of perfumes as you indulge your olfactory senses in some of the most unique fragrances the world has to offer.


Rare. Luxurious. Priceless — SCENTIDO brings together a collection of some of the most unique and sought after niche fragrances from around the world!

Derived from the Spanish word ‘Sentido’ – meaning sense, or heartfelt, SCENTIDO is the luxurious door you knock upon every time you set out to explore the art of perfumes.


Handpicked from France to New York, Italy to London, these perfumes will charm you into becoming a connoisseur.

We invite you on a fragrant journey to discover your personal expression through the art of scent with SCENTIDO Niche Perfumery, the first of its kind, experiential luxury boutique in India.


Come with us on a journey to the mysterious and imaginative worlds behind these miasmic marvels.
